<li><strong>Avoid heavy text overlays.</strong> Google may reject images that look like advertisements.</li>
</ul>
<h2>How Often to Post on Google Business Profile</h2>
<p>The minimum effective frequency is 1 post per week. That keeps your profile active and ensures you always have a recent post visible in search results.</p>
